//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0001>"Alright, I have to hurry."
<enT0001>"Alright, I have to hurry."

//TEXT
<jaT0002>As he left the lounge, Ryota breathed a sigh. He had no time, but he still wound up staying too long. As a result, he was most certainly late.
<enT0002>As he left the lounge, Ryota breathed a sigh. He had no time, but he still wound up staying too long. As a result, he was most certainly late.

//TEXT 【Long-haired Girl】
<jaT0003>"Ryota-kun?"
<enT0003>"Ryota-kun?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0004>"Huh? Oh, Nagase-san"
<enT0004>"Huh? Oh, Nagase-san"

//TEXT
<jaT0005>His eyes blinked with surprise when she called him. Her name was Nagase Sayaka. She was elected Chairman of the Student Council at the last election.
<enT0005>His eyes blinked with surprise when she called him. Her name was Nagase Sayaka. She was elected Chairman of the Student Council at the last election.

//TEXT
<jaT0006>She was obliging and sincere, so she was popular amongst both men and women. A fan club for this beauty was formed even in Ryota's class. So of course Ryota knew her name.
<enT0006>She was obliging and sincere, so she was popular amongst both men and women. A fan club for this beauty was formed even in Ryota's class. So of course Ryota knew her name.

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0007>"Hey, Ryota-kun, have you seen a girl about this tall with short hair? She's wearing regular clothes and she's rather cute..."
<enT0007>"Hey, Ryota-kun, have you seen a girl about this tall with short hair? She's wearing regular clothes and she's rather cute..."

//TEXT
<jaT0008>Sayaka said, indicated a height of about her forehead.
<enT0008>Sayaka said, indicated a height of about her forehead.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0009>"A girl? No, I haven't seen her."
<enT0009>"A girl? No, I haven't seen her."

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0010>"I see... hmm?"
<enT0010>"I see... hmm?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0011>"Did something happen to her?"
<enT0011>"Did something happen to her?"

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0012>"Well, it's strange. I've been searching for half an hour since when we were supposed to meet, but she's nowhere to be found. My class is about to start soon, too..."
<enT0012>"Well, it's strange. I've been searching for half an hour since when we were supposed to meet, but she's nowhere to be found. My class is about to start soon, too..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0013>"Hmmm. That really is strange. The only places to search are inside the Aries."
<enT0013>"Hmmm. That really is strange. The only places to search are inside the Aries."

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0014>"Right? I wonder where she went..."
<enT0014>"Right? I wonder where she went..."

//TEXT
<jaT0015>Sayaka looked down, full of worry.
<enT0015>Sayaka looked down, full of worry.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0016>"Alright, if I see her, I'll call out and tell her you're looking for her."
<enT0016>"Alright, if I see her, I'll call out and tell her you're looking for her."

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0017>"Thanks. That'll help."
<enT0017>"Thanks. That'll help."

//TEXT
<jaT0018>She smiled tenderly with appreciation.
<enT0018>She smiled tenderly with appreciation.

//TEXT 【Sayaka】
<jaT0019>"Then I'll be off, Ryota-kun"
<enT0019>"Then I'll be off, Ryota-kun"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0020>"Yea, Bye bye."
<enT0020>"Yea, Bye bye."

//TEXT
<jaT0021>After a little bow to Ryota as he waved, Sayaka left.
<enT0021>After a little bow to Ryota as he waved, Sayaka left.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0022>"That is strange. It's like she was spirited away."
<enT0022>"That is strange. It's like she was spirited away."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0023>"But, what's stranger is why did Nagase-san know my name? My first name, no less..."
<enT0023>"But, what's stranger is why did Nagase-san know my name? My first name, no less..."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0024>"Hmm. Well, whatever. I have to hurry to the meeting place."
<enT0024>"Hmm. Well, whatever. I have to hurry to the meeting place."

//TEXT
<jaT0025>Ryota took a glance at his watch as he spoke.@
<enT0025>Ryota took a glance at his watch as he spoke.@

//TEXT
<jaT0026>\nHe had anticipated being a little late, but after that second delay, he was now hopelessly past late.
<enT0026>\nHe had anticipated being a little late, but after that second delay, he was now hopelessly past late.

//TEXT
<jaT0027>Now it would be better to head directly to where class is being held. With that thought, Ryota changed course and ran for the Sheratan's Manufacturing Hangar.
<enT0027>Now it would be better to head directly to where class is being held. With that thought, Ryota changed course and ran for the Sheratan's Manufacturing Hangar.

//TEXT
<jaT0028>......
<enT0028>......

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0029>"I'm sorry I'm late!"
<enT0029>"I'm sorry I'm late!"

//TEXT
<jaT0030>Ryota arrived and bowed his head deeply. However, there was no response.
<enT0030>Ryota arrived and bowed his head deeply. However, there was no response.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0031>"Uwha? Now that I look, no one's here."
<enT0031>"Uwha? Now that I look, no one's here."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0032>"That's weird. Don't tell me they left me behind?"
<enT0032>"That's weird. Don't tell me they left me behind?"

//TEXT
<jaT0033>He looked around, but the hangar was silent. There were no traces of people. Despite his shortcut directly here, it looked like everyone had already left.
<enT0033>He looked around, but the hangar was silent. There were no traces of people. Despite his shortcut directly here, it looked like everyone had already left.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0034>"A-are you serious? It's mean to cast away people who are late!"
<enT0034>"A-are you serious? It's mean to cast away people who are late!"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0035>"Dammit!"
<enT0035>"Dammit!"

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0036>"Ryota-san"
<enT0036>"Ryota-san"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0037>"Ha? Wah!! I'm sorry!"
<enT0037>"Ha? Wah!! I'm sorry!"

//TEXT
<jaT0038>A voice interrupted his tirade, and Ryota leapt several inches.
<enT0038>A voice interrupted his tirade, and Ryota leapt several inches.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0039>"Huh? Oh, It's you, Cellaria-sensei. I'm certainly not..."
<enT0039>"Huh? Oh, It's you, Cellaria-sensei. I'm certainly not..."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0040>"Save it for later. There's something I need to ask you."
<enT0040>"Save it for later. There's something I need to ask you."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0041>"Where is your brother right now?"
<enT0041>"Where is your brother right now?"

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0042>"Huh? Brother? You mean Aniki?"
<enT0042>"Huh? Brother? You mean Aniki?"

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0043>"Yes. Tell me where Shuhei-san is, quickly."
<enT0043>"Yes. Tell me where Shuhei-san is, quickly."

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0044>"U-umm... He was in the lounge on the Sheratan..."
<enT0044>"U-umm... He was in the lounge on the Sheratan..."

//TEXT 【Cellaria】
<jaT0045>"Thank you."
<enT0045>"Thank you."

//TEXT
<jaT0046>After saying thanks, Cellaria jogged out of the room.
<enT0046>After saying thanks, Cellaria jogged out of the room.

//TEXT 【Ryota】
<jaT0047>"Wh-what was that all about? She looked awfully rushed."
<enT0047>"Wh-what was that all about? She looked awfully rushed."

//TEXT
<jaT0048>Ryota stared dumbfounded at the automatic door Cellaria exited through.
<enT0048>Ryota stared dumbfounded at the automatic door Cellaria exited through.

